snippet.textDisplay:
Hey TierZoo.


Long-time fan of yours (since 5k subs). In light of the recent months, I thought it would be a great idea if you could release a microbial tierlist (doesn't need to be solely pathogens). This would definitely be a daunting task, but that would really make us microbiologists happy! Since single-celled organisms play a huge role in maintaining the earth's global ecosystem and have dominated Earth's history so long as there existed life, it would be nice to give the families and clades of bacteria or even viral clades some love! I think this could also be a good chance to release a PSA on social distancing and make more people aware of the science and details behind the viral life-cycle of covid-19!


Jonathan
